Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Modern two level office development located within the heart of the West Leederville commercial precinct.

The first floor offices overlook Railway Parade and provide fantastic natural light. The side core lobby allows for easy separation of the floor to multiple tenants.

The building provides an opportunity for a prospective tenant to  provide excellent exposure and branding for their business.

Available via sub-lease or direct lease via negotiation.  

Head Lease Expiry: 30 June 2022.

Colin Gilchrist 0410 336 241

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: 278 RAILWAY PARADE - BOUTIQUE FIRST FLOOR OFFICES

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
The property comprises a three level office building positioned on the corner of Oxford Close and Bermondsey Street. The building occupies an enviable location in proximity to West Leederville Train Station, numerous bus routes and the freeway system.

Current vacancy:

Mezzanine - 154.9: Open plan office with strong natural light featuring a large boardroom & comms unit.  


Level 1 – 307.10: Fully fitted and self contained tenancy incorporating a meeting room, boardroom, open plan work stations, kitchen, storage and ablutions.


Level 2 – 310.90:  Fully fitted and self contained tenancy incorporating a meeting room, boardroom, open plan work stations, kitchen, storage and ablutions. 

 
Features include excellent natural light and whole floor tenancies available to smaller occupiers.

Both levels with on floor End of Trip facilities.

The building has low building outgoings, currently estimated at $100/sqm for the 2021/22 financial year.
 
Secure onsite basement car bays and open bays available.


For any queries, please contact the exclusive agents.

17-19 Oxford Close, West Leederville -

Boutique office accommodation positioned within a freestanding two level building, occupying an enviable fringe CBD location with excellent transport links.

Well positioned near public transport and access to both the freeway north & south.

Multiple self-contained suites available, comprising a mixture of partitioned and open plan accommodation.

Ground - 189sqm - open plan;
Level 1 - 197sqm;
Level 1 - 196sqm;

TOTAL - 582sqm.

Functional accommodation with flexible layouts available.

Low outgoings payable by the Lessee.

High Parking Availability!
